content:
The Field Service Analytics app brings the power of Analytics to Salesforce Field Service on any device that supports CRM Analytics.

With intuitive visualizations based on your field service data, Field Service Analytics provides just-in-time analytics for field service managers and dispatchers. You get clear data insights to improve every on-site experience. Field Service Analytics empowers managers with answers to help their technicians deliver personalized, actionable customer service.

Follow the steps in the order shown to get started with Field Service Analytics. If you havenâ€™t used CRM Analytics before, learn more about it from the Analytics Documentation.

The Field Service Analytics app includes prebuilt dashboards to accelerate Field Service data exploration.

Set up Field Service Analytics app permissions, make sure your org is enabled to use Field Service, and assign field level security correctly so you can create and share the app.
title: Field Service Analytics: Unlocking Insights with CRM
